---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Beranda TSL">
<main>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-xl pb-24 bg-surface">
<div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-xl">
<div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
<h1 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg md:text-display-lg text-primary mb-md">
                        Tarbiyah Sunnah Learning: Belajar Islam, Al-Qur’an, dan Bahasa Arab secara <span class="text-tertiary">Bertahap, Terarah, dan Bermakna.</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-body-lg font-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-xl max-w-2xl">
                        Akses pendidikan Islam berkualitas melalui sistem pembelajaran daring dan luring yang amanah, dirancang untuk mendukung pertumbuhan spiritual Anda setiap langkah.
                    </p>
<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-sm justify-center md:justify-start">
<button class="bg-tertiary text-on-tertiary px-xl py-md rounded-lg font-title-lg text-title-lg hover:opacity-90 transition-all">
                            Lihat Program
                        </button>
<button class="border-2 border-primary text-primary px-xl py-md rounded-lg font-title-lg text-title-lg hover:bg-primary/5 transition-all">
                            Masuk LMS TSL
                        </button>
<button class="bg-surface-container-high text-primary px-xl py-md rounded-lg font-label-md text-label-md flex items-center gap-xs">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="info">info</span>
                            Sistem Informasi Qur’an
                        </button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 w-full max-w-lg">
<div class="aspect-square bg-surface-container-low rounded-3xl relative overflow-hidden border border-outline-variant">
<img alt="Learning Experience" class="w-full h-full object-cover grayscale-[0.5]" data-alt="A serene, minimalist classroom environment with natural lighting streaming through large windows. The scene captures a clean, wooden desk with a leather-bound book and a digital tablet, symbolizing the blend of traditional and modern learning. The aesthetic is corporate yet warm, using a soft green and white color palette to create a peaceful atmosphere. No human faces are visible." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDbdO-JT-QCF6h4lOzkVb128kMMpWL2Pg4hsLG-H5SVHXTba8Y4H6ImYC2IEtsIe8GkJfko9mHGqIx1o2c3uEDoBU4BCLHkHippK7CgZ7M_t8wn4YkF2_4PK5yxuQ8Nq_Fnm7wRDqrerv-IxfOyCFhB2yKc4fL5AAzQ2wYTNDs3aun_Gm786AdeDaLQh3xbEi7jhg6qBFVI5tab35bKxphfi1S5tAcEJ48KBlhs5MLpXFEvoAGmrza5ORnIIguTKn0GeDptv_9duwUV">
<div class="absolute bottom-md left-md right-md bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm p-sm rounded-xl flex items-center gap-sm border border-primary/10">
<div class="w-xs h-xs bg-tertiary-fixed-dim rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-tertiary-container" data-icon="trending_up">trending_up</span>
</div>
<span class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface">5,000+ Siswa Aktif Bertumbuh</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Program Showcase - Bento Grid Inspired -->
<section class="py-xl bg-surface-container-lowest">
<div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="text-center mb-xl">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-primary mb-xs">Program Pendidikan Kami</h2>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Pilih jalur belajar yang sesuai dengan kebutuhan Anda saat ini.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-gutter">
<!-- Ma’had TSL -->
<div class="group bg-surface border border-outline-variant p-md rounded-xl hover:border-primary transition-all flex flex-col h-full">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-sm" data-icon="school">account_balance</span>
<h3 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg text-on-surface mb-xs">Ma’had TSL</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant flex-grow mb-md text-sm">Program pendidikan Islam berjenjang yang mencakup Aqidah, Fiqh, dan Akhlak.</p>
<button class="text-primary font-label-md text-label-md flex items-center gap-xs group-hover:gap-sm transition-all">
                            Pelajari Program <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" data-icon="arrow_forward">account_balance</span>
</button>
</div>
<!-- S-1 PJJ -->
<div class="group bg-surface border border-outline-variant p-md rounded-xl hover:border-primary transition-all flex flex-col h-full">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-sm" data-icon="auto_stories">history_edu</span>
<h3 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg text-on-surface mb-xs">S-1 PJJ</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant flex-grow mb-md text-sm">Pendidikan Jarak Jauh setingkat Sarjana dengan kurikulum yang terstandarisasi.</p>
<button class="text-primary font-label-md text-label-md flex items-center gap-xs group-hover:gap-sm transition-all">
                            Pelajari Program <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" data-icon="arrow_forward">history_edu</span>
</button>
</div>
<!-- Arabic Online -->
<a href="/kelas-bahasa-arab" class="group bg-surface border border-outline-variant p-md rounded-xl hover:border-primary transition-all flex flex-col h-full">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-sm" data-icon="translate">language</span>
<h3 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg text-on-surface mb-xs">Arabic Online</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant flex-grow mb-md text-sm">Kuasai Bahasa Arab dari dasar hingga tingkat lanjut dengan metode praktis.</p>
<span class="text-primary font-label-md text-label-md flex items-center gap-xs group-hover:gap-sm transition-all mt-auto">
                            Pelajari Program <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" data-icon="arrow_forward">language</span>
</span>
</a>
<!-- Qur’an Kids -->
<div class="group bg-surface border border-outline-variant p-md rounded-xl hover:border-primary transition-all flex flex-col h-full">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-sm" data-icon="child_care">child_care</span>
<h3 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg text-on-surface mb-xs">Qur’an Kids</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant flex-grow mb-md text-sm">Metode menyenangkan bagi anak-anak untuk mencintai dan menghafal Al-Qur’an.</p>
<button class="text-primary font-label-md text-label-md flex items-center gap-xs group-hover:gap-sm transition-all">
                            Pelajari Program <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" data-icon="arrow_forward">child_care</span>
</button>
</div>
<!-- Qur’an Adults -->
<div class="group bg-surface border border-outline-variant p-md rounded-xl hover:border-primary transition-all flex flex-col h-full">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-sm" data-icon="menu_book">auto_stories</span>
<h3 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg text-on-surface mb-xs">Qur’an Adults</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant flex-grow mb-md text-sm">Tahsin dan Tahfidz khusus dewasa dengan bimbingan ustadz yang berpengalaman.</p>
<button class="text-primary font-label-md text-label-md flex items-center gap-xs group-hover:gap-sm transition-all">
                            Pelajari Program <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" data-icon="arrow_forward">auto_stories</span>
</button>
</div>
<!-- Madrasah Kids Online -->
<div class="group bg-surface border border-outline-variant p-md rounded-xl hover:border-primary transition-all flex flex-col h-full">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-sm" data-icon="skillet">smart_toy</span>
<h3 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg text-on-surface mb-xs">Madrasah Kids Online</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant flex-grow mb-md text-sm">Pembentukan karakter islami dan pengetahuan dasar agama untuk anak usia dini.</p>
<button class="text-primary font-label-md text-label-md flex items-center gap-xs group-hover:gap-sm transition-all">
                            Pelajari Program <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" data-icon="arrow_forward">smart_toy</span>
</button>
</div>
<!-- Basic Islam (BID) -->
<div class="group bg-surface border border-outline-variant p-md rounded-xl hover:border-primary transition-all flex flex-col h-full">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-sm" data-icon="lightbulb">foundation</span>
<h3 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg text-on-surface mb-xs">Belajar Islam Dasar (BID)</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant flex-grow mb-md text-sm">Pondasi dasar bagi siapa saja yang ingin memulai belajar Islam secara benar.</p>
<button class="text-primary font-label-md text-label-md flex items-center gap-xs group-hover:gap-sm transition-all">
                            Pelajari Program <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" data-icon="arrow_forward">foundation</span>
</button>
</div>
<!-- Online Lectures -->
<div class="group bg-surface border border-outline-variant p-md rounded-xl hover:border-primary transition-all flex flex-col h-full">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-sm" data-icon="video_library">cast_for_education</span>
<h3 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg text-on-surface mb-xs">Kajian Rutin Online</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant flex-grow mb-md text-sm">Kajian tematik rutin yang dapat diakses kapan saja dari mana saja.</p>
<button class="text-primary font-label-md text-label-md flex items-center gap-xs group-hover:gap-sm transition-all">
                            Pelajari Program <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" data-icon="arrow_forward">cast_for_education</span>
</button>
</div>
<!-- Offline Collaboration -->
<div class="group bg-surface border border-outline-variant p-md rounded-xl hover:border-primary transition-all flex flex-col h-full">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl mb-sm" data-icon="groups">groups</span>
<h3 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg text-on-surface mb-xs">Kegiatan Kolaborasi Offline</h3>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant flex-grow mb-md text-sm">Daurah dan temu muka untuk mempererat ukhuwah dan pendalaman materi.</p>
<button class="text-primary font-label-md text-label-md flex items-center gap-xs group-hover:gap-sm transition-all">
                            Pelajari Program <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" data-icon="arrow_forward">arrow_forward</span>
</button>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- "Mulai dari Mana?" Section -->
<section class="py-xl bg-primary text-on-primary">
<div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-xl">
<div class="flex-1">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg mb-md">Mulai dari Mana?</h2>
<p class="text-body-lg font-body-lg mb-xl opacity-90">Kami membantu Anda menemukan langkah pertama yang tepat sesuai dengan niat dan kondisi Anda.</p>
<div class="space-y-sm">
<a class="flex items-center justify-between p-md bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-xl transition-all border border-white/20" href="#">
<span class="font-title-lg text-title-lg">Saya ingin belajar Bahasa Arab dari nol</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="chevron_right">chevron_right</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center justify-between p-md bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-xl transition-all border border-white/20" href="#">
<span class="font-title-lg text-title-lg">Saya ingin memperbaiki bacaan Al-Qur'an</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="chevron_right">chevron_right</span>
</a>
<a class="flex items-center justify-between p-md bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-xl transition-all border border-white/20" href="#">
<span class="font-title-lg text-title-lg">Saya ingin anak saya belajar agama sejak dini</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined" data-icon="chevron_right">chevron_right</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 hidden md:block">
<img alt="Guide" class="rounded-3xl shadow-xl rotate-3" data-alt="A focused image of an open notebook with neatly written notes and a pen placed on its spine, resting on a clean white surface. Soft shadows and warm morning light create a sense of beginning and preparation. The color theme features muted greens and cream tones to evoke a scholarly and calm mood, aligning with the concept of a new learning journey." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuAwtunWeH6A1RSEBjxf1PveGD02L23Ay1pGKRDT3YyDauN70irtbYZf_7yvYM0dBcE8PxJkARg9FTqmP8HcwUg-8RvN9Cmz0hUi0Bq8X6J0J_hU1P25Nn67DRoKicYe9q_g2fGl4ZX49EVKMF7oVpMOG_1wTekWB6WqJUD_3X1TwydgauJc5rtxN5upW2cTh80xVaNhGTm76pPKSMRx9O1eroHUJkXjXo2K1BS3GAOv-NAmaqlfZjY9eWOhWcX9hxlTvuPG178W98mA">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- "Mengapa TSL?" -->
<section class="py-xl bg-surface">
<div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="text-center mb-xl">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-primary">Mengapa Belajar di TSL?</h2>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-xl">
<div class="text-center">
<div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl" data-icon="stairs">stairs</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg mb-xs">Bertahap</h4>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Kurikulum yang disusun rapi langkah demi langkah.</p>
</div>
<div class="text-center">
<div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl" data-icon="explore">explore</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg mb-xs">Terarah</h4>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Visi pendidikan yang jelas dan terukur hasilnya.</p>
</div>
<div class="text-center">
<div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl" data-icon="schedule">schedule</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg mb-xs">Fleksibel</h4>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Sistem LMS yang dapat diakses kapan saja dan di mana saja.</p>
</div>
<div class="text-center">
<div class="w-20 h-20 bg-primary/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-md">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-4xl" data-icon="favorite">favorite</span>
</div>
<h4 class="font-title-lg text-title-lg mb-xs">Berbasis Adab</h4>
<p class="font-body-md text-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Mengutamakan penanaman nilai adab sebelum ilmu.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Alur Belajar -->
<section class="py-xl bg-surface-container-low overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<h2 class="font-headline-lg text-headline-lg text-primary text-center mb-xl">Alur Belajar yang Mudah</h2>
<div class="relative flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:justify-between gap-xl md:gap-0">
<!-- Line -->
<div class="hidden md:block absolute top-10 left-0 w-full h-1 bg-tertiary-fixed-dim -z-0"></div>
<!-- Steps -->
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-sm md:w-1/5">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white border-4 border-tertiary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold">1</div>
<span class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface text-center">Pilih Program</span>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-sm md:w-1/5">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white border-4 border-tertiary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold">2</div>
<span class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface text-center">Pendaftaran</span>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-sm md:w-1/5">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white border-4 border-tertiary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold">3</div>
<span class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface text-center">Orientasi Siswa</span>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-sm md:w-1/5">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white border-4 border-tertiary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold">4</div>
<span class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface text-center">Proses Belajar</span>
</div>
<div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-sm md:w-1/5">
<div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white border-4 border-tertiary rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-primary font-bold">5</div>
<span class="font-label-md text-label-md text-on-surface text-center">Evaluasi Akhir</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Jadwal Terdekat & Artikel -->
<section class="py-xl bg-surface">
<div class="max-w-max-width mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-xl">
<!-- Upcoming Schedule -->
<div>
<div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-md">
